    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to a range of bright medium greens to dark bluish green colors resembling the color of emerald, a mineral used as a gemstone.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
